'''珀魯'''（{{lang|en|'''Peru'''}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[學托擴縣_(堪薩斯州)|學托擴縣]]轄下的城市<ref name="GNIS"/>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有139人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=November 3, 2011|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
珀魯設立於1870年<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA155#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=155 | access-date=2016-05-12 | archive-date=2017-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215110908/https://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA155#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此城市的名字由公司總裁E·R·卡特勒（E. R. Cutler）以他位在[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]的故鄉{{le|珀魯 (伊利諾伊州)|Peru, Illinois|珀魯}}來命名<ref>{{cite book|last=Rydjord|first=John|title=Kansas Place-Names|url=https://archive.org/details/kansasplacenames0000rydj|year=1972|publisher=University of Oklahoma Press, Norman, Oklahoma|isbn=0-8061-0994-7|page=[https://archive.org/details/kansasplacenames0000rydj/page/98 98]& 280}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4941 | title=Profile for Peru, Kansas | publisher=[[ePodunk|ePodunk]] | accessdate=6 June 2014 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050536/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=4941 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==地理==
珀魯坐落於北緯37度4分53秒、西經96度5分47秒（亦可表示為37.081299, -96.096277）處<ref name="GNIS"/>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|0.83|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

